description:
Moses had some issues: His temper was out of control. He was impulsive. And he could let fear get the best of him. But Ron Whitehead tells Kenia Reyes that Moses always came back to God. Moses was a Bible hero because he was faithful to Gods call and led the Israelites out of Egypt. No matter how bad we mess things up, we too can always come back to God.

Learn more about Moses and lots of other inspiring Bible characters by playing Heroes 2: the Bible Trivia Game.

Learn more at https://www.heroesbibletrivia.org/en/
